[color=#ffffff]Una volta scaricato il file si può installare con NMM. Dentro al gioco avviare la console premendo il tasto \, quindi scrivere showracemenu e premere INVIO.
[/color]Nel menu PRESETS digitare F9 e caricare Jacline.
Il file Jacline Race Menu imperiale-HDT utilizza i capelli KS Hairdos nella versione HDT.
Ho usato un corpo CBBE HDT modificato da me che troverete nei file opzionali.
[/size]

[size=2]For this preset I have used the following mod:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?] KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?] SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22701/?] Seductive Lips HD[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59192/?] Eyes of Aber[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?] True Eyes[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?] Brows[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/31665/?] Better Makeup for SKSE[/url]


Once the file is downloaded you can install with NMM. Into the game start the console by pressing the \ key, then write showracemenu and press ENTER.
In the PRESETS menu, type F9 and load Jacline.
The Jacline Race Menu Imperiale-HDT uses the KS Hairdos hair in the HDT version.
I used a body CBBE HDT modified by me that you will find in the optional files.
[/size]
